== 評價 ==
《功夫熊貓3》獲得了普遍好評，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於178條評論，新鮮度87%，平均分為6.90/10，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到66分，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得7.3分。
爛番茄共识：「功夫熊貓3擁有必要的輝煌[[視覺|視覺]]，但不像它圓嘟嘟的[[主角|主角]]，這部[[續集|續集]]的故事出奇的敏捷，是部值得全家[[娛樂|娛樂]]的[[電影|電影]]。」

== 制作 ==
2010年，[[夢工廠動畫公司|梦工厂动画]]首席执行官{{link-en|Jeffrey Katzenberg|Jeffrey Katzenberg}}宣布功夫熊猫系列一共有6部<ref name=Future>{{cite news|last=O'Hara|first=Helen|title=Katzenberg Talks DreamWorks Sequels|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=29638|accessdate=September 7, 2011|newspaper=Empire|date=December 3, 2010|archive-date=2011-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110531191349/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=29638|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年7月，梦工厂动画首席创意官Bill Damaschke官方确认了《功夫熊猫3》<ref>{{cite news|last=Oldham|first=Stuart|last2=Maxwell|first2=Erin|title=Comic-Con: D'Works fires up 'Kung Fu Panda 3'|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118056504|accessdate=July 12, 2012|newspaper=Variety|date=July 12, 2012|archive-date=2012-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120817090927/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118056504|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本片将由梦工厂动画和[[东方梦工厂|东方梦工厂]]（2012年由[[上海市|上海]]由梦工厂动画和上海東方傳媒集團工作室联合成立）联合制作，三分之一将在中国制作，其余将在美国梦工厂动画制作<ref name=SeekingAlphaQ32012>{{cite news |title=DreamWorks Animation SKG Management Discusses Q3 2012 Results - Earnings Call Transcript |url=http://seekingalpha.com/article/971501-dreamworks-animation-skg-management-discusses-q3-2012-results-earnings-call-transcript?page=4&p=qanda&l=last |accessdate=November 26, 2012 |newspaper=Seeking Alpha |date=November 1, 2012 |archive-date=2013-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130413071322/http://seekingalpha.com/article/971501-dreamworks-animation-skg-management-discusses-q3-2012-results-earnings-call-transcript?page=4&p=qanda&l=last |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=THRProduction />。这是美国主导的动画电影第一次同中国公司联合制作<ref name=PRNXuhui>{{cite press release|author1=DreamWorks Animation|title=Rising Dreams in the Orient: Oriental DreamWorks To Establish Headquarters in Xuhui|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/rising-dreams-in-the-orient-oriental-dreamworks-to-establish-headquarters-in-xuhui-165209436.html|publisher=PR Newswire|accessdate=December 10, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204165459/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/rising-dreams-in-the-orient-oriental-dreamworks-to-establish-headquarters-in-xuhui-165209436.html|archivedate=2012-12-04|date=August 6, 2012|deadurl=no}}</ref>。制片公司正与[[中国国家新闻出版广电总局|国家新闻出版广电总局]]亲密合作以确保影片在中国的发行<ref name=NYT011413>{{cite news|title=To Get Movies Into China, Hollywood Gives Censors a Preview|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/15/business/media/in-hollywood-movies-for-china-bureaucrats-want-a-say.html|accessdate=January 15, 2013|newspaper=The New York Times|date=January 14, 2013|author=Michael Cieply|author2=Brooks Barnes|archive-date=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216015305/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/15/business/media/in-hollywood-movies-for-china-bureaucrats-want-a-say.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。作为一部与中国的合拍片，梦工厂可以避免中国大陸严格的进口配额限制，并能分享比进口影片更大比例的票房收益<ref name=DeadlineChinaStatus>{{cite web|last1=Jaafar|first1=Ali|title=‘Kung Fu Panda 3′ To Get China Co-Production Status|url=http://deadline.com/2015/01/kung-fu-panda-3-to-get-china-co-production-status-1201356517/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=March 7, 2015|date=January 23, 2015|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702203659/http://deadline.com/2015/01/kung-fu-panda-3-to-get-china-co-production-status-1201356517/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=THRProduction>{{cite news|last=Tsui|first=Clarence|title='Kung Fu Panda 3' to Begin Production in August|url=http://rewired.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kung-fu-panda-3-begin-569896|accessdate=June 17, 2013|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=June 17, 2013|archive-date=2013-06-19|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130619233932/http://rewired.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kung-fu-panda-3-begin-569896|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。为了确保影片在中国的成功，除了英语版以外，中文版也将完全动画化，使之成为唯一一个声音与口型同步的外语版本<ref name=VarietyPumpsUp>{{cite news|last1=Frater|first1=Patrick|title=Jeffrey Katzenberg Pumps Up ‘Panda 3,’ Puts Down Deal Talk|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jeffrey-katzenberg-kung-fu-panda-1201475355/|accessdate=April 19, 2015|work=Variety|date=April 19, 2015|archive-date=2015-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711043209/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jeffrey-katzenberg-kung-fu-panda-1201475355/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本片由[[詹妮弗·余·尼尔森|詹妮弗·余·尼尔森]]执导，Melissa Cobb制片，{{link-en|Jonathan Aibel|Jonathan Aibel and Glenn Berger}}及{{link-en|Glenn Berger|Jonathan Aibel and Glenn Berger}}编剧，以及{{link-en|Glenn Berger|Jonathan Aibel and Glenn Berger}}担任联合制片<ref name=Slate2016>{{cite news |title=New Distributor Twentieth Century Fox Unveils DreamWorks Animation's Release Slate Through 2016 |url=http://ir.dreamworksanimation.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=705761 |accessdate=September 10, 2012 |newspaper=DreamWorks Animation |date=September 9, 2012 |author=DreamWorks Animation |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20131012035253/http://ir.dreamworksanimation.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=705761 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。del Toro在一次新闻发布会上表示该片的反派角色将是“有史以来最强大的反派”<ref>{{cite news |last=Chitwood |first=Adam |title=Guillermo del Toro Talks Puss in Boots 2, Kung Fu Panda 3 & Trollhunters; Says Panda 3 Has the 'Most Formidable Villain in the Series' |url=http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-sequel-kung-fu-panda-3-guillermo-del-toro/210271/ |accessdate=November 12, 2012 |publisher=Collider.com |date=November 12, 2012 |archive-date=2014-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318041406/http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-2-sequel-kung-fu-panda-3-guillermo-del-toro/210271 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年4月9日，官方宣布[[瑞贝尔·威尔森|瑞贝尔·威尔森]]、[[布萊恩·克蘭斯頓|布萊恩·克蘭斯頓]]及[[邁茲·米克森|邁茲·米克森]]将参演本片<ref name=PRNCranston />。

2015年2月，有消息称{{link-en|Alessandro Carloni|Alessandro Carloni}}将与[[詹妮弗·余·尼尔森|詹妮弗·余·尼尔森]]联合执导本片。据该报道，首部电影担任动画主管，第二部担任故事艺术家的Carloni加盟[[詹妮弗·余·尼尔森|詹妮弗·余·尼尔森]]，并根据其要求“强化后台”以确保该片及时完工<ref name=DeadlineCodirector>{{cite web|last1=Patten|first1=Dominic|title=‘Kung Fu Panda 3′ Gets Co-Director As DWA Looks To Shore Up Franchises|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/kung-fu-panda-3-director-alessandro-carloni-jennifer-yuh-1201378811/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=February 28, 2015|date=February 24, 2015|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708235129/http://deadline.com/2015/02/kung-fu-panda-3-director-alessandro-carloni-jennifer-yuh-1201378811/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

